      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MORE RAIN (2) is having his first look at this track. Comes here a last start placegetter at The Gardens in a Grade 5 (22.88). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Must come into calculations. MOJAVE (1) was safely held in tougher company last start at Maitland, but prior to that won by 2.5 lengths at Maitland (25.06) beating Digger Sure Can in a Grade 5 on March 30. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Likely to play a prominent role. BLUE FRECKLE (8) was strongly fancied to break through last time and justified the confidence with a maiden win at this track over 388m (22.38). Will break from a wide draw. Bold showing expected again. SAVVY LAD (7) cannot be ruled out.",
